&lt;p&gt;what they mean is no, you can&apos;t.
there is no way to get it done.
so it was possible you could do something like this&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-js s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title function_&quot;&gt;create&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-params&quot;&gt;obj, &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;){
